<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٧٨٨ - فَقَدْ رُوِّينَا، عَنْ عِكْرِمَةَ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهَا مُحْكَمَةٌ غَيْرُ مَنْسُوخَةٍ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٢٧٨٩ - وَكَذَلِكَ عَنْ أَبِي مُوسَى الْأَشْعَرِيِّ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>